      "name": "CVE-2025-55182",
      "description": "React2Shell is a vulnerability affecting Node.js applications that allow user-supplied JSON data to influence internal JavaScript object structures. Improper validation enables attackers to escalate this into remote command execution via access to process.mainModule.require and child_process.execSync.",
